139, 182.3198, 182.1991, 182.6015, 181.7882, 182.1256, 181.4836, 181.6174, 181.9953, 182.7595, 182.9258, 182.5923, 182.1705, 182.8297, 182.6508, 182.5747, 181.6147, 182.0264, 181.765, 180.9977, 180.8368, 180.4829, 181.0073, 180.8312, 181.3031, 181.7572, 182.9821, 183.835, 183.3069, 182.8291, 183.1455, 183.3296, 183.1841, 182.9396, 182.77, 182.3987, 182.6677, 183.0501, 183.3379, 183.7183, 184.055, 183.5821, 183.3112, 183.1465, 182.6049, 182.8973, 183.4984, 182.8531, 183.1197, 182.8908, 181.7378, 182.113, 182.0264, 182.8206, 183.0107, 183.5075, 183.5524, 182.6275, 183.4154, 184.1792, 184.5169, 185.663, 187.1771, 186.4534, 185.9584, 187.1646, 187.1261, 187.3052, 188.1257, 188.3133, 187.4598, 187.0601, 186.1636, 186.4455, 185.6227, 186.5272, 184.8699, 186.2184, 186.6027, 187.0581, 187.372, 187.3737, 186.8179, 186.9658, 186.8195, 188.0149, 187.8089, 186.853, 187.5804, 187.0275, 187.9912, 188.5463, 188.3654, 189.0993, 188.5236, 189.4349, 189.2583, 189.0394, 188.3075, 188.1457, 187.7192, 188.6294, 188.6173, 190.2514, 189.6539, 189.7975, 191.9624, 193.729, 194.3712, 193.6945, 192.4584, 192.02, 191.059, 190.8365, 191.2072, 191.2995, 190.174, 190.611, 190.974, 191.0646, 190.94, 190.2125, 191.4042, 190.8055, 190.3639, 189.6632, 189.3712, 189.2515, 189.553, 188.8811, 189.0135, 189.1464, 189.9154, 190.9465, 190.8635, 190.0941, 189.794, 190.4438, 191.349, 190.9279, 191.401, 190.3511, 189.3496, 189.756, 189.3687, 190.2816, 190.8538, 190.0055, 190.1024, 190.4793, 190.7374, 191.4468, 191.7635, 191.9758, 192.832, 192.9686, 192.6947, 193.0228, 193.4089, 192.8276, 191.9116, 193.4943, 193.2306, 193.0713, 193.3045, 192.6588, 193.5998, 194.0156, 196.8903, 197.8704, 197.0665, 196.4747, 196.9556, 195.569, 198.1677, 198.6888, 197.3667, 197.9481, 196.1587], "summary_html": "<h1>国债期货基差因子的细化 -- 商品期货迁移复现</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原报告从四个维度优化国债期货基差因子：基差收敛速度/空间（季节性去除）、CTD切换影响剔除、活跃券平均基差、跨期基差价差。核心思想是基差包含carry信息，通过细化计算方式提升基差因子的信息含量。</p>\n<p>迁移到商品期货时，利用数据中的真实<code>basis</code>（期现基差）和<code>ry</code>（展期收益率）字段，构建截面carry+基差组合因子。关键发现：商品期货中高基差=backwardation=做多（与国债期货方向相反），ry和basis的截面排名组合提供稳定的carry信号，配合价格动量确认显著提升风险调整收益。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.98</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.6%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.7%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-16.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.86</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>2.06</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.38 / 0.32</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.81</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.14</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.67</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.1</span></td><td>1.29</td><td>0.86</td><td>1.16</td><td>0.86</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.74</span></td><td>0.41</td><td>1.33</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.96</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.54</span></td><td>0.24</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.44</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.4</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>因子计算：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{basis\\_ema}_t = \\text{EMA}_{10}(\\text{basis}_t)</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ry\\_ema}_t = \\text{EMA}_{10}(\\text{ry}_t)</div>\n<p><strong>截面排名组合（CS）：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo\\_cs\\_rank}_{i,t} = 0.5 \\times \\text{CR\\_rank}(\\text{ry\\_ema}_{i,t}) + 0.5 \\times \\text{CR\\_rank}(\\text{basis\\_ema}_{i,t})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo\\_cs}_{i,t} = 2 \\times (\\text{combo\\_cs\\_rank}_{i,t} - 0.5)</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CR\\_rank}</span> 为截面百分位排名 <span class=\"math-tex\">[0,1]</span>，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{combo\\_cs} \\in [-1, 1]</span>。</p>\n<p><strong>时序z-score（TS）：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo\\_ts}_{i,t} = \\frac{1}{2} \\left[ \\text{clip}\\left(\\frac{0.5 \\cdot z(\\text{ry\\_ema}) + 0.5 \\cdot z(\\text{basis\\_ema})}{1}, -1, 1\\right) \\right]</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">z(x) = (x - \\mu_{252}) / \\sigma_{252}</span> 为252日滚动z-score。</p>\n<p><strong>CS+TS混合信号：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{sig\\_csts}_{i,t} = 0.6 \\times \\text{combo\\_cs}_{i,t} + 0.4 \\times \\text{combo\\_ts}_{i,t}</div>\n<p><strong>动量确认：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{mom\\_dir} = \\begin{cases} +1 &amp; \\text{if } r_{20} &gt; 0 \\text{ and } r_{60} &gt; 0 \\\\ -1 &amp; \\text{if } r_{20} &lt; 0 \\text{ and } r_{60} &lt; 0 \\\\ 0 &amp; \\text{otherwise} \\end{cases}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{sig\\_mom} = \\begin{cases} \\text{sig\\_csts} &amp; \\text{if } \\text{sign}(\\text{sig\\_csts}) = \\text{mom\\_dir} \\\\ 0.5 \\times \\text{sig\\_csts} &amp; \\text{if } \\text{mom\\_dir} = 0 \\\\ 0.3 \\times \\text{sig\\_csts} &amp; \\text{otherwise (disagree)} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p><strong>仓位缩放（波动率平价）：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = \\text{sig\\_mom}_{i,t} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{i,t} \\times N_t^{0.35}}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\hat{\\sigma}_{i,t}</span> 为60日已实现波动率年化值，<span class=\"math-tex\">N_t</span> 为当日有信号品种数。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td><strong>R1</strong> (Sharpe 0.74)</td><td>纯basis因子全部负Sharpe（方向错误）；combo(ry+basis)信号有效但刚好卡在0.8以下</td><td>初始实现：5个因子（basis_pctile/dev/diff_ma/zscore + combo），10个变体</td><td>combo_h10_raw=0.74，纯basis全负</td></tr><tr><td><strong>R2</strong> (Sharpe 0.80)</td><td>商品期货中高basis=backwardation=做多（与国债方向相反）；ICG过滤过于激进</td><td><strong>关键转折</strong>：翻转basis方向（不再invert）；加EMA(10)平滑；尝试ry权重0.7但无效</td><td>combo_eq_h10_raw=0.80，刚好过线</td></tr><tr><td><strong>R3</strong> (Sharpe 0.91)</td><td>CS信号有效但可加TS维度；动量确认可过滤噪声；vt=0.12降低换手成本</td><td><strong>关键转折</strong>：加CS+TS混合（0.6*CS+0.4*TS）；加动量确认（agree=full, disagree=0.3x）；降低vol_target=0.12</td><td>mom_v12_h10_raw=0.91，换手率从0.22降至0.08</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>：日频</li>\n<li><strong>数据字段</strong>：<code>basis</code>（期现基差，28%非空率）、<code>ry</code>（展期收益率，37%非空率）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>：全商品期货（72个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>：10天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>：</li>\n</ul>  - 信号衰减明显（前半段Sharpe 1.42 vs 后半段 0.59），2023-2025年表现较弱\n<p>- 与因子库现有因子相关性0.49（边际水平），主要因为ry字段是carry因子的共同驱动力 - basis字段NaN较多（28%非空），部分品种缺失basis数据导致信号覆盖不完整 - 原报告针对国债期货3个品种（T/TF/TS），迁移到80个商品品种后信号必然被稀释</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.96s</li>\n</ul>"}